@startuml
actor Client
participant "ClubController\n(DTO Layer)" as ClubController
participant "ClubService\n(Business Logic)" as ClubService
participant "ClubRepository\n(Entity Layer)" as ClubRepository
database DB

Client -> ClubController : POST /clubs\nclubDTO
note right of ClubController: Validación automática del DTO\n(@Valid, @NotNull, etc.)

ClubController -> ClubService : createClub(clubDTO)
note right of ClubService: Aplica lógica de negocio:\n- Mapea DTO -> Entity\n- Reglas de negocio (ej.: nombre único)

ClubService -> ClubRepository : save(club)
ClubRepository -> DB : INSERT INTO club ...
DB --> ClubRepository : OK / generated id
ClubRepository --> ClubService : Club entity

ClubService --> ClubController : ClubDTO
ClubController --> Client : 201 Created\nclubDTO

@enduml
